+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The only hard dependency is UnderscoreJS. For RESTful persistence and DOM manip-
ulation, include jQuery.


+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Versions
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

jQuery 3.2,
UnderscoreJS 1.8.3
BackboneJS 1.3.3

+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Overview
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

BackboneJS consists of five main objects:

Models, Collections, Views, Routers, Events

+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
that & this
+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Note that even Backbone suffers from context issues. Often you will find that
Backbone application store current context is self or that.